text: Phintella caledoniensis is a jumping spider species in the genus Phintella that was first identified in 2009. It is the first species from the genus to be identified in New Caledonia. ==References== Category:Fauna of New Caledonia Category:Salticidae Category:Spiders described in 2009 Category:Spiders of Oceania
title: Phintella caledoniensis
